PRODUCT DATA 2:
Title: Samba Shoes | adidas US
Content: Price $100. Samba OG Shoes.What are adidas Sambas shoes for? The adidas Samba is a soccer shoe first introduced in 1950, designed for training, futsal and street soccer. Its gum rubber outsole with pivot points offers great traction for nimble movements.
Source: https://www.adidas.com/us/samba
